Our Services






Legacy Planning
Creating an optimal strategy for your estate is more than just managing estate taxes … it’s about organizing your assets so they pass to your family, loved ones or a charity in the manner you wish.  It’s about maximizing how much you leave behind, while still ensuring that your financial needs are taken care of for the rest of your life.







Social Security
Many people trigger their Social Security benefit at the wrong time. Don’t be one of them! We will provide you with the information and tools you need to help you know when and how to file so you can maximize your lifetime benefit.
Legacy Wealth Management, Inc. and Legacy Associates, Inc. are not affiliated with or endorsed by the Social Security Administration or any government agency.







Retirement Planning
Legacy Wealth Management, Inc. takes pride in providing comprehensive retirement planning services to our clients. We review our clients wills, estate plans/trusts, taxes, and insurance. Our comprehensive services integrate all aspects of our client’s financial picture in a coordinated effort to provide for financial clarity and multi-generational wealth.







Investment Management
At Legacy Wealth Management, Inc., we believe no two investors are alike. In order to help each client meet their financial goals, we use a personalized approach to investing. Our advice and recommendations are tailored to our clients’ investment goals, desired return objectives, risk tolerance, time horizon, and income needs. Our investment strategies are designed based on your investment goals.
Legacy Wealth Management, Inc. does not offer legal or tax planning services or advice, but has a strategic alliances with independent tax or legal advisors to provide accounting, legal and tax services.








